email in >

- rules -

- from address
    - equal to
    - contains
    - not equal to

- to address
    - equal to
    - contains
    - not equal to

- subject
    - equal to
    - contains
    - not equal to

- body
    - equal to
    - contains
    - not equal to

- actions - (allow multiple actions per rule, store values in temp variable)
    - send (body, subject, from address, to address) to api (get, post)
    - get url
    - send email
    - read xml
    - read json
    - trim from (subject, body)
    
